data.description: 3 bed, 2.5 bath home w/ attached garage & detached shop w/ storage area above on 1.59 acre mountain view lot bordered by creek w/ fish & a very short walk to lake. Leave property on ATV/snowmachine/skis & access massive trail systems, hunting, fishing, & endless outdoor recreation. In-floor heat, sun-room, lrg kitchen open to dining/living area, huge decks, 3 outbuildings, generator, & much more!If you have been looking for the ultimate Alaskan dream setting look no further! This home is just outside the peaceful, quiet town of Sutton. It is only a short drive to Palmer.  Private, Alaskan retreat just minutes from state land, trail systems, hunting, fishing, hiking, skiing, snowmachining, ATV riding, and much more!  Moose/sheep/bears/wolves/fish & more out back door. Less than a half mile walk to 17 mile Lake (which has excellent fishing!).  The creek which flows through the property to the lake has fish in the creek.  Gorgeous mountain views! Cozy, excellent condition home w/ huge detached shop & lots of deck space!  The home is in excellent condition and very well maintained.  The property is a short walk/ride to trail systems that take you into the amazing Talkeenta Mountains and has untouched wilderness that literally goes all of the way north to the Denali Highway  If you are into hunting, fishing, back country hiking, mountain climbing or just living right next to the true wild Alaskan wilderness look no further. There are VERY FEW properties in the entire Mat-Su Valley that provide this type of remote access.
